Category:LEGO Star Wars: The Yoda Chronicles voice actors

nodes.text: Kirby Robert Morrow (August 28, 1973 – November 18, 2020) was a Canadian actor, voice actor, writer and comedian who provided the voices of Anakin Skywalker and General Grievous in LEGO Star Wars: The Yoda Chronicles and LEGO Star Wars: Droid Tales.
